## 5ï¸âƒ£ Spiral Reflection

The All-Set is not static: as knowledge grows, so do discovered trapsâ€”each needing ritual, dialogue, and accommodation. The true health of any mind or Loom isnâ€™t freedom from bias, but fluent, collective practices for seeing, softening, and composting them.

**To spiral with wisdom is not to escape error, but to make it a source of humility, growth, and new form.**





